{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-markdown-js","path":"/components/ez-form-layout","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Form layouts are used to arrange fields within a form using standard spacing. Fields are stacked vertically, but can be further grouped into rows using the <code>EzLayout</code> component.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><EzAlert\n  headline=\"This component is under development\"\n  tagline=\"There will likely be breaking changes to the API. Proceed with caution.\"\n  use=\"warning\"\n/></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"best-practices\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#best-practices\" aria-label=\"best practices permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Best Practices</h2>\n<p>Forms should:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Follow a predicable order, guiding the user to fill out the most important content first</li>\n<li>Group related tasks under section titles to provide more context and make the form easier to scan</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"examples\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-label=\"examples permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h2>\n<h3 id=\"standard-form-layout\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#standard-form-layout\" aria-label=\"standard form layout permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Standard form layout</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">&#x3C;EzFormLayout>\n  &#x3C;EzField type=\"text\" label=\"First name\" />\n  &#x3C;EzField type=\"text\" label=\"Last name\" />\n  &#x3C;EzField type=\"number\" label=\"Favorite Number\" value={7} />\n&#x3C;/EzFormLayout>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"field-groups\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#field-groups\" aria-label=\"field groups permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Field groups</h3>\n<p>Use <code>EzLayout</code> to arrange multiple fields into a row or to vary form field layout across various breakpoints.</p>\n<p>Typically used to group familiar layouts such as state and zip code, or start/end dates. Fields that are not directly related to each other should not be grouped next to each other as this makes it easier to miss at a glance.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">&#x3C;EzFormLayout>\n  &#x3C;EzLayout layout=\"basic\">\n    &#x3C;EzField type=\"text\" label=\"First name\" />\n    &#x3C;EzField type=\"text\" label=\"Last name\" />\n  &#x3C;/EzLayout>\n&#x3C;/EzFormLayout>\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"related-components\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#related-components\" aria-label=\"related components permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Related components</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/recipe/components/ez-field\">EzField</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipe/components/ez-layout\">EzLayout</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipe/components/ez-alert\">EzAlert</a></li>\n</ul>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Form layouts are used to arrange fields within a form using standard spacing. Fields are stacked vertically, but can be further grouped into rows using the "},{"type":"element","tagName":"code","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"EzLayout"}]},{"type":"text","value":" component."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"hr","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"ezalert","properties":{"headline":"This component is under development","tagline":"There will likely be breaking changes to the API. Proceed with caution.","u